"Fight through corridors and gardens, and dominate the eastern courtyard of "
"what used to be the glorious city of Elensefar."
msgstr ""
"在迴廊與花園之間殺出一條血路，並支配那個曾經輝煌過的城市──艾倫索法的東側庭"
"院。"

