"Warfare transforms the simple farms and villages of a peaceful region into a "
"subtly parceled battlefield. Designed by Doc Paterson."
msgstr ""
"戰爭把平凡的農場和和平的村莊轉變為一塊巧妙劃分的戰場。由Doc Paterson設計。"

