#: data/multiplayer/scenarios/8p_Morituri.cfg:7
msgid ""
"Teamwork and tactics are key to victory in this unusual battlefield, where "
"eight armies fight to the finish."
msgstr "在這片不尋常的戰場上，8支軍隊要對抗到底，團隊合作與戰術是致勝關鍵。"

